query: SELECT e.id, e.gamePresenterId, gp.name, gp.teamId, DATE_FORMAT(e.evaluationDate, '%Y-%m-%d') as evalDate, e.totalScore FROM evaluations e LEFT JOIN game_presenters gp ON e.gamePresenterId = gp.id ORDER BY e.id DESC LIMIT 30;
